Class GVRPickerInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRHybridObject

        • org.gearvrf.GVRBehavior

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GVRDrawFrameListener

    public class GVRPickerInput
extends GVRPicker
    Finds the first scene object that is hit by a ray to dispatch hover events or touch events to it. User can register implementations of IHoverEvents or ITouchEvents to GVRSceneObject.getEventReceiver() to handle these events.
